import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    x_coordinates = data['x']
    plt.hist(x_coordinates, bins=20, color='blue', alpha=0.7, label='x-coordinates')
    plt.axvline(x_coordinates.median(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=2, label=f'Median: {x_coordinates.median():.2f}')
    plt.xlabel('X-Coordinates')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of the x-coordinates of the points?', wrap=True)
    plt.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.hist(data['y'], bins=20, color='blue', alpha=0.7, label='y-coordinates')
    plt.axvline(data['y'].median(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=2, label=f"Median: {data['y'].median():.2f}")
    plt.xlabel('Y-coordinates')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of the y-coordinates of the points?', wrap=True)
    plt.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.scatter(data['x'], data['y'])
    plt.xlabel('x')
    plt.ylabel('y')
    plt.title('Is there a correlation between the x and y coordinates of the points?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.hist(data['point_sizes'], bins=20, color='blue', alpha=0.7, edgecolor='black')
    plt.xlabel('Point Sizes')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of the point sizes?', wrap=True)
    plt.axvline(data['point_sizes'].median(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=2, label=f"Median: {data['point_sizes'].median():.2f}")
    plt.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    color_counts = data['color'].value_counts()
    color_counts.plot(kind='bar', color=color_counts.index)
    plt.xlabel('Point Colors')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of the point colors?', wrap=True)
    plt.legend(color_counts.index, title='Colors')
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
